            "faq_question": "Q1. What are the four main types of diamonds?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>The four main scientific types of diamonds are Type Ia, Type Ib, Type IIa, and Type IIb, classified based on the presence and arrangement of nitrogen and boron impurities.</p>"
