          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "Q3. What are type 2 diamonds?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Type II (or type 2) diamonds are diamonds that have no measurable nitrogen impurities, which makes them exceptionally rare in nature but common among high-quality lab-grown diamonds.</p>"
